lead_paragraph: Week 9 is another difficult one for fantasy owners with the Bears, Bengals, Cardinals, Patriots, Redskins and Texans on their bye. Since you'll likely be delving a bit deeper into the depth charts, keep in mind that another eight teams still have their break coming up; four in Week 10 and another four in Week 11.

headline.print_headline: FANTASY PLAYS: West, Smith, Henry and Other Week 9 Pickups
